Path: godot/classes/class_physicsmaterial.rst
Summary: Defines physics properties for surfaces, including roughness and bounciness, to be applied to physics bodies.

Holds physics-related properties of a surface, namely its roughness and bounciness. This class is used to apply these properties to a physics body.
