Document: PhysicsMaterial
Path: godot/classes/class_physicsmaterial.rst
Summary: Overview of PhysicsMaterial class properties and their default values

- absorbent (bool): Determines if the material is absorbent. Default: false
- bounce (float): Controls the bounce coefficient of the material. Default: 0.0
- friction (float): Defines the friction coefficient of the material. Default: 1.0
- rough (bool): Indicates if the material surface is rough. Default: false
